<!--more-->

<h3 id="gcp-compute-engine-instance">GCP Compute Engine instance</h3>

<p>Create instance: <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcloud compute instances create INSTANCE_NAME</code><br />
Start instance: <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcloud compute instances start INSTANCE_NAME</code><br />
List instances: <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcloud compute instances list</code><br />
Stop instance: <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcloud compute instances stop INSTANCE_NAME</code><br />
Delete instance: <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcloud compute instances delete INSTANCE_NAME</code></p>

<p>*Commands can work with multiple instances by separating instance names by space</p>
